2017-10-14 20-00-00:
	Title: Release 20171014
	Author: Paul Chote
	Content: After three months of public playtesting we are pleased to finally declare "Mission Accomplished" on the new OpenRA release! Changes include:\n\n  • New game launchers supporting side-by-side installs\n  • A new command-bar interface for your units\n  • Overhauled building targeting and damage systems\n  • Improved support for LAN games\n  • Replay and map editor improvements\n  • Community-driven balance updates to RA and TD\n  • Many other performance and bug fixes\n\nHead to www.openra.net for more information and to download the new release! We hope you enjoy it!